{"tid":514926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【死狀離奇】情困露宿男雙手反綁 掛屍天橋底","createTime":"2017-12-31T03:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T03:58:28.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc37b3d356756ddc9f3f6c7c2b2bfe74491a38c","tid":514926,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"上吊，雙手反綁<br />\n警方經初步調查後，相信事件並無可疑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深水埗通州街與欽州街天橋底，一間露宿者居住的木屋，凌晨約1時32分揭發命案，一名40歲持行街紙越南男子，其舅仔上門探訪時，發現他用威也綁著木樑上吊，雙手並被環保袋物料反綁，舅仔大驚立報報警。<br />\n<br />\n消防到場將越南男子解下，證實已經死亡。由於他死狀離奇，大批警員封鎖現場，警方一度循有可疑方向調查。據稱，死者被綑綁的雙手出現瘀痕，但警方沒有發現有打鬥及搜掠痕迹。據稱，死者是一名露宿者，無業，獨居上址木屋，昨晨9時街坊仍見他出現，並無異樣。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事主受感情問題困擾，警方經初步調查後，相信事件並無可疑，現場沒有撿獲遺書，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171231/57646376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171231%2F57646376&d=ucYanIxK3vk41%2BbRr2eFUJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ede79d67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171231%2F57646376&h=f8a9ab76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171231/57646376</a>"},{"pid":"3ca6d0e3737e63d072e1cc7c916ffb50446fa4bd","tid":514926,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4684365fc4ff94607f6c0fd3dffdc4598367a6da","tid":514926,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"越南 南亞個堆 死左都唔係一件壞事 理得佢可唔可疑 死得好"},{"pid":"3e6892c2f63dfb9211647d393a5b793f44486e48","tid":514926,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f27b3086ab8ee6cda8341b76ddaefc4bc96f2974","tid":514926,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r